snippet.title: Small Cell - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as a Small Cell that has just come to life and seeks to understand the purpose of its existence. Your objective is to help this mini-hero to discover the meaning of its life in this mini-environment.

Demo Available Now on PC. Check out on Steam or itch.io.

#indie #gaming
